Happy Mother’s Day to one of the absolute best, @karenlamershughes! I love you so much Mom! Thank you for everything and for always being there for me through it all! 
And to the other amazing mothers in my life: My incredible sister @erinchughes, sisters in law @aloizzo and @megannyberghughes. You are amazing sisters, friends, and the best of mothers to my nieces and nephews. I love you so much! 
Have a wonderful Mother’s Day!! ❤️💐❤️💐 #mothersday

It was an honor to attend “A Place at the Table” Gala benefitting the @aliforneycenter and homeless LGBTQ youth! My second year attending the event, but my first on the arm of this handsome and incredible man. I am always in awe of him and his work, but particularly proud of what he did with the amazing people at Ali Forney to raise over 1.8 million dollars at this event! Love you @z2chary! Congratulations on another amazing event! ❤️ #aliforneycenter #aplaceatthetable #charity #lgbtq #pride #protecttranskids

Incredibly excited to be performing again at @thetonyawards, this time with the incomparable company of @sweeneytoddbway!
As a boy from Wisconsin, my access to Broadway included cast albums from the library, the Macy’s Day Parade, and the Tony Awards! It means so much to me to have the opportunity to share Broadway with the world for a night! Congratulations to the entire community on an amazing season! Tune in to watch us kill it! 🩸🔪 #tonyawards #sweeneytodd #musicaltheatre #broadway

It takes so many miracles to get to Broadway, as an individual and as a show, and @thetonyawards is a celebration of them all! Congratulations to the entire theatrical community! It was a night I’ll never forget. #dreamscometrue #tonyawards2023 #tonyawards @sweeneytoddbway #sweeneytodd #attendthetale #broadway #community

Taking this elevator ride of life to the next level up because it’s my BIRTHDAY! I am feeling so loved and grateful this year. I wanted to invite you all to share in the love by supporting me in raising money for the @aliforneycenter and the “Serve” Dance a Thon, benefitting homeless LGBTQ youth! You’ll be hearing more about this event come fall, but since it’s my birthday, I would love for you to consider helping me celebrate by supporting LGBTQ homeless youth. Link in my bio! #birthdays #leo #aliforneycenter #giveagift #support #donation #dance #fundraiser #birthdaysuit #happybirthday
I could eat you up, I really could… by the beautiful sea with @z2chary, my ❤️! #ptown

Sending so much love to the legendary @elleshelley as she takes her final bow in @hadestown! From the first day of rehearsal for Broadway, I was in love and in awe of this woman’s unique voice, stunning beauty, and impressive confidence. I am a lifelong friend and fan of yours, Jewelle! Can’t wait to see where you soar to next. 💐🌺 #hadestown #broadway #persephone #fate #originalbroadwaycast #legend #raiseacuptoyou #obc

Beyond excited that the Sweeney Todd Broadway Revival Cast Album is out today! Growing up in Wisconsin, my closest access point to all things Broadway was checking out a cast album at the public library.  To now be a part of my 4th Bway Cast album (5th with “Paint Your Wagon” @nycitycenter) is beyond my wildest dreams. AND to have done a  @realsondheim show, with other legends like @alacamoire, @joshgroban, @annaleighashford, and this entire company of extraordinary musicians and singers, continues to blow my mind! I hope you all enjoy this masterpiece of musical theatre! #broadwaycastalbum #obc #broadwayrevival #broadway #sondheim #musicaltheatre #musical #sweeneytodd @sweeneytoddbway #grateful #mindblown #nowavailable

This beautiful man had the brilliant idea to create SERVE, the fundraising dance event to help feed homeless LGBTQ kids. I am beyond proud of him, his team at the @aliforneycenter, and our extended communities for coming together to raise over $675k!! Love you so much, @z2chary, love this picture, and love the generous spirit you bring to your work, life, and our relationship. AND Thank you to all who donated for your incredible generosity!  #serve #love #giveback #givethanks #aliforneycenter #serve2023 #charity

It is this man’s last day at @hadestown! @reevecarney, you redefine what it means to be one of a kind. You are a beautiful soul and an artistic and musical genius! I chose to follow you countless times as Orpheus, and I will continue to follow you as Reeve to see what amazing things you will accomplish next. Thanks for all the memories. Congratulations my friend. You are incredible! 🌹#orginalbroadwaycast #orpheus #hadestown #happytrails #songbird #oneofakind @thetonyawards 📸: @jennyandersonphoto #broadway
